OL,3,C'Madness': Justice Minister fury over
OL,4,Cparamilitary engagement plan
OL,6,FUK and Irish Governments plan to
OL,7,Fappoint an independent figure to
OL,8,Fexamine whether a formal process of
OL,9,Fengagement with paramilitary groups in
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland is required to bring
OL,11,Fabout their disbandment.
OL,13,FHowever, the Justice Minister has
OL,14,Fcalled the proposal "madness".
