OL,3,C'Madness': Justice Minister fury over
OL,4,Cparamilitary engagement plan
OL,6,F"Could you imagine the government
OL,7,Fengaging in this way with any other
OL,8,Fcriminal gang? It's unthinkable and
OL,9,Fyet these are criminal gangs
OL,10,Fcommitting offences that are causing
OL,11,Fharm in our community in the here and
OL,12,Fnow," she said.
OL,14,FIt comes after the Independent
OL,15,FReporting Commission (IRC) said in its
OL,16,Flatest report that a "twin track"
OL,17,Fprocess of law enforcement and
OL,18,Ftackling the roots of paramilitarism
OL,19,Fis needed.
