OL,3,C'Madness': Justice Minister fury over
OL,4,Cparamilitary engagement plan
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland Secretary Hilary Benn
OL,7,Fhas insisted no financial offer will
OL,8,Fbe made to paramilitary groups to
OL,9,Fpersuade them to end violence.
OL,11,FIn its seventh report, the IRC
OL,12,Freiterated its call for the two
OL,13,FGovernments to appoint an independent
OL,14,Fperson to scope out what a formal
OL,15,Fprocess of engagement and group
OL,16,Ftransition might look like.
OL,18,FIn response, Mr Benn said the two
OL,19,FGovernments have been "giving
OL,20,Fconsideration to how progress could be
OL,21,Fmade towards ending paramilitarism".
OL,26,@{D@WOU}D@cO]
