OL,3,C'Madness': Justice Minister fury over
OL,4,Cparamilitary engagement plan
OL,6,FHe said: "The two Governments have
OL,7,Fagreed to jointly appoint, in the
OL,8,Fperiod ahead, within the existing IRC
OL,9,Flegislative framework, an independent
OL,10,Fexpert to carry out a short scoping
OL,11,Fand engagement exercise to assess
OL,12,Fwhether there is merit in, and support
OL,13,Ffor, a formal process of engagement to
OL,14,Fbring about paramilitary group
OL,15,Ftransition to disbandment.
OL,17,F"This will include examining what
OL,18,Fcould be in scope of such a formal
OL,19,Fprocess."
OL,26,@nD@JOUyD@AOU{D@IO]
