OL,6,FMr Benn added: "I want to be clear
OL,7,Fthat this is not the start of a formal
OL,8,Fprocess itself.
OL,10,F"This scoping exercise is also not a
OL,11,Fpart of, nor an alternative to, the
OL,12,Fexisting law enforcement and criminal
OL,13,Fjustice measures and the wider effort
OL,14,Fthrough the Executive Programme to
OL,15,Ftackle the ongoing violence and harm
OL,16,Fcaused by paramilitary groups.
OL,26,@nD@POUrD@AOU
