OL,6,F"I also want to be clear that no
OL,7,Ffinancial offer will be made to
OL,8,Fparamilitary groups or to the
OL,9,Findividuals involved in them in
OL,10,Fexchange for an end to violence and
OL,11,Fongoing harms."
OL,13,FThe IRC's report said it had been a
OL,14,F"mixed year" in the region, with a
OL,15,Fdecease in shootings and paramilitary-
OL,16,Fstyle assaults, but "concerning levels
OL,17,Fof intimidation, coercive control and
OL,18,Fthreats".
