OL,6,FThe body ` led by commissioners John
OL,7,FMcBurney, Monica McWilliams, Tim
OL,8,FO'Connor and Mitchell Reiss ` was
OL,9,Festablished in 2017 to report annually
OL,10,Fon progress towards ending
OL,11,Fparamilitary activity in the region.
OL,13,FIt is governed by an international
OL,14,Ftreaty between the UK and Irish
OL,15,FGovernments which reflected the terms
OL,16,Fof the Fresh Start Agreement concluded
OL,17,Fby the two Governments and the
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland parties in 2015.
