OL,3,C'Madness': Justice Minister fury over
OL,4,Cparamilitary engagement plan
OL,6,FIn a statement following the seventh
OL,7,Freport, the commissioners described
OL,8,F"shifting dynamics" within both
OL,9,Frepublican and loyalist paramilitary
OL,10,Fgroups.
OL,12,FThey said: "There has been a decrease
OL,13,Fin shooting incidents and paramilitary-
OL,14,Fstyle assaults. However, bombing
OL,15,Fincidents and casualties from
OL,16,Fparamilitary-style shootings have
OL,17,Fremained consistent with previous
OL,18,Fyears.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@SO]tD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/14
