OL,3,C'Madness': Justice Minister fury over
OL,4,Cparamilitary engagement plan
OL,6,F"Intimidation, coercive control and
OL,7,Fthreats linked to paramilitary groups
OL,8,Fpersist and remain a real concern.
OL,10,F"In 2024, we have seen shifting
OL,11,Fdynamics within both republican and
OL,12,Floyalist paramilitary groups,
OL,13,Fincluding changes in leadership,
OL,14,Freported splits, speculation about
OL,15,Fpossible feuds, ongoing questions
OL,16,Fabout whether actions were sanctioned
OL,17,Fby paramilitary leaders, various
OL,18,Finterpretations of larger gatherings
OL,19,Fof people, and increasing interactions
OL,20,Fwith organised crime.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU
