OL,3,C'Madness': Justice Minister fury over
OL,4,Cparamilitary engagement plan
OL,6,F"We understand that this can be
OL,7,Fchallenging for the PSNI and others in
OL,8,Fattributing responsibility for, or
OL,9,Finvolvement in, certain actions.
OL,10,FHowever, where there is paramilitary
OL,11,Finvolvement, this must be called out
OL,12,Fand the harm it causes has to be
OL,13,Fnamed."
OL,15,FThe commissioners also emphasised the
OL,16,Fneed for a "twin track" approach of
OL,17,Ftackling paramilitarism as well as a
OL,18,Fformal process of group transition.
