OL,3,C'Madness': Justice Minister fury over
OL,4,Cparamilitary engagement plan
OL,6,FThey said: "Track one comprises a
OL,7,Frobust and targeted set of law
OL,8,Fenforcement measures addressing
OL,9,Fparamilitarism, coupled with an
OL,10,Feffective wider criminal justice
OL,11,Fresponse.
OL,13,F"Track two involves a comprehensive
OL,14,Ftackling of the deep-rooted socio-
OL,15,Feconomic conditions which are linked
OL,16,Fto the continuing existence of
OL,17,Fparamilitarism today.
OL,19,F"Both tracks, which are inter-related,
OL,20,Fare vital in the task of tackling and
OL,21,Fending paramilitarism.
OL,26,@nD@LOUuD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/14
