OL,3,C'Madness': Justice Minister fury over
OL,4,Cparamilitary engagement plan
OL,6,F"Our report advocates for a third
OL,7,Fdimension to complement the twin-track
OL,8,Fapproach: an agreed formal process of
OL,9,Fgroup transition, involving direct
OL,10,Fengagement with the paramilitary
OL,11,Fgroups themselves, in order to bring
OL,12,Fabout their ending."
OL,14,FThe commissioners also welcomed the
OL,15,Ffocus on paramilitarism in the new
OL,16,Fdraft Programme for Government of the
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland Executive.
