OL,6,FThey said: "We strongly recommend that
OL,7,Fsome of the targeted paramilitary-
OL,8,Ffocused work which the programme has
OL,9,Fbeen responsible for should continue
OL,10,Fbeyond 2027, while also ensuring that
OL,11,Fconsideration is given to those
OL,12,Felements of the work of tackling
OL,13,Fparamilitarism that could be
OL,14,Fintegrated into mainstream policies."
OL,16,FPolice Service of Northern Ireland
OL,17,F(PSNI) Assistant Chief Constable Davy
OL,18,FBeck welcomed the IRC report.
